WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue {
font-size: 1em;
font-weight: bold;
color: #ffffff;
}

00:01:31.180 --> 00:01:34.700 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:01:34.820 --> 00:01:37.700 line:80%
=Episode 25=

00:01:38.820 --> 00:01:39.700 line:80%
How has he treated you

00:01:40.290 --> 00:01:41.210 line:80%
these past half a month?

00:01:44.340 --> 00:01:45.370 line:80%
He's treated me

00:01:47.460 --> 00:01:48.300 line:80%
well.

00:01:52.010 --> 00:01:53.180 line:80%
And how do you feel about him?

00:01:57.850 --> 00:01:58.690 line:80%
I...

00:02:00.570 --> 00:02:02.010 line:80%
Do you like him?

00:02:11.740 --> 00:02:12.900 line:80%
I do.

00:02:14.690 --> 00:02:16.300 line:80%
When I broke off the engagement with Yuqi,

00:02:17.210 --> 00:02:18.490 line:80%
I didn't feel sad.

00:02:21.020 --> 00:02:22.300 line:80%
But when I think

00:02:23.460 --> 00:02:25.620 line:80%
that I might never see Mu Qingyan again,

00:02:28.620 --> 00:02:30.340 line:80%
my heart feels empty,

00:02:33.180 --> 00:02:34.020 line:80%
it hurts.

00:02:39.970 --> 00:02:40.810 line:80%
Zhao,

00:02:42.060 --> 00:02:43.780 line:80%
now that your engagement is dissolved,

00:02:44.060 --> 00:02:45.060 line:80%
in principle,

00:02:45.460 --> 00:02:46.620 line:80%
who you choose to be with

00:02:46.860 --> 00:02:48.090 line:80%
is up to you.

00:02:48.580 --> 00:02:49.650 line:80%
If that boy truly is

00:02:50.060 --> 00:02:51.490 line:80%
a child of the Chang family,

00:02:51.690 --> 00:02:53.300 line:80%
your mother and I would be very pleased.

00:02:53.300 --> 00:02:54.170 line:80%
But

00:02:54.210 --> 00:02:55.050 line:80%
don't forget,

00:02:55.900 --> 00:02:57.580 line:80%
he is the young master of the demon sect.

00:02:57.930 --> 00:02:58.770 line:80%
What of it?

00:02:59.930 --> 00:03:01.970 line:80%
Are there any fewer vile people
among the Six Sects?

00:03:04.490 --> 00:03:06.490 line:80%
There are plenty of vile people
in the Six Sects.

00:03:06.690 --> 00:03:08.020 line:80%
Yin Dai is the first that comes to mind.

00:03:08.340 --> 00:03:09.210 line:80%
And that Wang Yuanjing,

00:03:09.530 --> 00:03:11.090 line:80%
he deserves to die ten times over.

00:03:11.900 --> 00:03:12.740 line:80%
But Zhao,

00:03:13.530 --> 00:03:14.370 line:80%
is Mu Qingyan

00:03:14.580 --> 00:03:15.690 line:80%
necessarily a good man?

00:03:16.310 --> 00:03:17.650 line:80%
You forgot the story your master told you

00:03:17.650 --> 00:03:18.650 line:80%
about the skin-painted demon?

00:03:18.650 --> 00:03:20.140 line:80%
Mu Qingyan may not be that demon.

00:03:20.620 --> 00:03:21.580 line:80%
And didn't your aunt

00:03:21.580 --> 00:03:23.410 line:80%
once think the same?

00:03:31.690 --> 00:03:32.650 line:80%
What do you mean?

00:03:37.650 --> 00:03:38.780 line:80%
Mother?

00:03:39.620 --> 00:03:41.530 line:80%
This concerns your aunt's reputation.

00:03:42.090 --> 00:03:44.140 line:80%
If you weren't facing the same situation now,

00:03:44.140 --> 00:03:45.860 line:80%
we would have taken this secret to our graves.

00:03:52.460 --> 00:03:53.300 line:80%
Back then,

00:03:53.810 --> 00:03:55.690 line:80%
your aunt, your master,

00:03:56.530 --> 00:03:57.580 line:80%
and your Uncle Lei,

00:03:57.970 --> 00:03:59.140 line:80%
seven of them in all,

00:04:00.530 --> 00:04:01.860 line:80%
secretly trained in a formation

00:04:01.860 --> 00:04:03.970 line:80%
derived from the Big Dipper Formation.

00:04:04.970 --> 00:04:06.020 line:80%
Once completed,

00:04:06.460 --> 00:04:08.140 line:80%
even Nie Hengcheng would have struggled
against it.

00:04:08.580 --> 00:04:09.810 line:80%
But unexpectedly,

00:04:10.300 --> 00:04:11.580 line:80%
aside from your master and your aunt,

00:04:11.930 --> 00:04:12.930 line:80%
the other five

00:04:13.410 --> 00:04:14.460 line:80%
were ambushed

00:04:14.460 --> 00:04:15.340 line:80%
before the final battle.

00:04:16.020 --> 00:04:17.850 line:80%
Your Uncle Lei survived,

00:04:18.050 --> 00:04:20.020 line:80%
but was left crippled for life.

00:04:20.700 --> 00:04:22.650 line:80%
The place where the seven of them hid,

00:04:22.650 --> 00:04:23.850 line:80%
aside from themselves,

00:04:24.170 --> 00:04:25.580 line:80%
only one other person knew.

00:04:27.530 --> 00:04:28.370 line:80%
The skin-painted demon?

00:04:30.410 --> 00:04:32.460 line:80%
So the cold case Uncle Tieqiao mentioned

00:04:33.700 --> 00:04:35.050 line:80%
was his doing?

00:04:35.850 --> 00:04:37.340 line:80%
Now you understand why your aunt

00:04:38.090 --> 00:04:39.170 line:80%
charged off without hesitation

00:04:39.170 --> 00:04:40.970 line:80%
to kill Nie Hengcheng back then.

00:04:41.460 --> 00:04:42.580 line:80%
That demon had caused the deaths

00:04:43.050 --> 00:04:45.290 line:80%
of the brothers who shared life and death
with her.

00:04:45.290 --> 00:04:46.190 line:80%
How could her heart

00:04:46.200 --> 00:04:47.210 line:80%
not be torn apart?

00:04:47.700 --> 00:04:48.730 line:80%
With the formation ruined,

00:04:50.210 --> 00:04:51.580 line:80%
she had no choice

00:04:52.940 --> 00:04:54.610 line:80%
but to face the demon alone.

00:04:55.700 --> 00:04:57.850 line:80%
Your aunt was killed by the skin-painted demon.

00:05:00.020 --> 00:05:01.170 line:80%
Where did he go afterward?

00:05:01.850 --> 00:05:03.460 line:80%
Your aunt only said he disappeared.

00:05:04.170 --> 00:05:05.820 line:80%
We know nothing more.

00:05:10.970 --> 00:05:11.810 line:80%
Zhao,

00:05:13.530 --> 00:05:14.820 line:80%
you've always had a mind of your own.

00:05:16.500 --> 00:05:17.610 line:80%
Learn from the past,

00:05:18.780 --> 00:05:20.820 line:80%
don't follow in your aunt's footsteps.

00:05:34.580 --> 00:05:36.730 line:80%
Remember what your master told you:

00:05:37.050 --> 00:05:37.900 line:80%
a demon

00:05:39.090 --> 00:05:40.650 line:80%
will devour people.

00:05:40.940 --> 00:05:42.580 line:80%
Mu Qingyan may not be that demon.

00:05:42.970 --> 00:05:43.940 line:80%
And didn't your aunt

00:05:43.940 --> 00:05:45.650 line:80%
once think the same?

00:06:18.340 --> 00:06:19.820 line:80%
(Nie Zhe has appeared in the Hanhai Mountains.)

00:06:20.190 --> 00:06:21.500 line:80%
(There may be clues about the man in black.)

00:06:21.500 --> 00:06:22.340 line:80%
(Three days from now,)

00:06:22.580 --> 00:06:23.420 line:80%
(I'll wait for you.)

00:06:23.730 --> 00:06:24.650 line:80%
Zhao.

00:06:24.650 --> 00:06:25.820 line:80%
Learn from the past,

00:06:26.820 --> 00:06:28.850 line:80%
don't follow in your aunt's footsteps.

00:06:45.210 --> 00:06:46.170 line:80%
(No need to wait.)

00:06:47.140 --> 00:06:48.850 line:80%
(I'll find the man in black myself.)

00:06:50.020 --> 00:06:51.410 line:80%
(The martial world has no set meeting.)

00:06:51.940 --> 00:06:53.340 line:80%
(Mr. Mu, take care.)

00:07:06.290 --> 00:07:07.130 line:80%
Milady,

00:07:07.410 --> 00:07:09.020 line:80%
why aren't you eating?

00:07:09.340 --> 00:07:10.180 line:80%
I'm not hungry.

00:07:11.170 --> 00:07:12.010 line:80%
Milady,

00:07:12.410 --> 00:07:14.020 line:80%
don't take those vile rumors

00:07:14.020 --> 00:07:15.730 line:80%
outside to heart.

00:07:15.730 --> 00:07:18.730 line:80%
It was clearly Mu Qingyan's
one-sided infatuation.

00:07:18.730 --> 00:07:19.820 line:80%
When he was at Qingque Sect,

00:07:19.820 --> 00:07:20.700 line:80%
I could tell

00:07:20.700 --> 00:07:22.210 line:80%
he was always clinging to you.

00:07:22.210 --> 00:07:24.090 line:80%
He is handsome, I'll grant him that,

00:07:24.090 --> 00:07:25.210 line:80%
but

00:07:25.210 --> 00:07:26.100 line:80%
I never imagined

00:07:26.120 --> 00:07:27.580 line:80%
he'd dare harbor improper thoughts about you.

00:07:27.580 --> 00:07:28.420 line:80%
Zhao.

00:07:32.140 --> 00:07:33.090 line:80%
Zhuo.

00:07:33.090 --> 00:07:33.930 line:80%
Xingjia.

00:07:38.410 --> 00:07:40.290 line:80%
I'll go brew some tea.

00:07:48.530 --> 00:07:49.370 line:80%
Zhao,

00:07:49.940 --> 00:07:51.050 line:80%
I roasted a chicken,

00:07:51.340 --> 00:07:52.180 line:80%
cumin-flavored.

00:07:53.090 --> 00:07:53.930 line:80%
Have a taste.

00:07:54.340 --> 00:07:55.900 line:80%
I truly have no appetite.

00:08:00.530 --> 00:08:04.820 line:80%
"My belt grows loose, yet I do not regret."

00:08:04.820 --> 00:08:08.340 line:80%
"For him, I grow haggard and worn."

00:08:14.020 --> 00:08:15.410 line:80%
Have you two lost your minds?

00:08:16.780 --> 00:08:17.630 line:80%
Zhao, we've thought it

00:08:17.700 --> 00:08:18.540 line:80%
over again and again.

00:08:18.970 --> 00:08:20.140 line:80%
Why not

00:08:21.290 --> 00:08:22.130 line:80%
forget about him?

00:08:23.650 --> 00:08:25.090 line:80%
Whether he's good or bad,

00:08:25.460 --> 00:08:27.460 line:80%
our master and your parents will never agree.

00:08:27.700 --> 00:08:28.970 line:80%
It's too hard.

00:08:29.650 --> 00:08:31.290 line:80%
Have you two nothing better to do?

00:08:32.930 --> 00:08:34.330 line:80%
If you follow Young Master Mu

00:08:34.330 --> 00:08:35.980 line:80%
and someday we stand on opposite sides
of a battle,

00:08:35.980 --> 00:08:37.780 line:80%
how are we supposed to face each other?

00:08:38.170 --> 00:08:40.620 line:80%
But if you marry Yuzhi instead,

00:08:41.170 --> 00:08:42.900 line:80%
the Six Sects of Beichen,

00:08:42.900 --> 00:08:45.020 line:80%
or at least three or four of them

00:08:45.020 --> 00:08:47.050 line:80%
could ensure mutual security
and advance together.

00:08:47.050 --> 00:08:48.620 line:80%
Old grudges could be resolved as well.

00:08:49.380 --> 00:08:50.330 line:80%
Wouldn't that be ideal?

00:08:50.810 --> 00:08:52.650 line:80%
I'll go see how Feicui's tea is coming along.

00:08:53.620 --> 00:08:54.690 line:80%
The chicken is all yours.

00:08:56.530 --> 00:08:58.650 line:80%
The ancestors of the Song family

00:08:59.050 --> 00:09:00.810 line:80%
have finally shown their favor.

00:09:02.650 --> 00:09:03.570 line:80%
This rascal

00:09:03.980 --> 00:09:06.100 line:80%
has finally come to his senses.

00:09:12.020 --> 00:09:13.170 line:80%
Only the timing

00:09:13.520 --> 00:09:14.370 line:80%
may not be ideal.

00:09:14.410 --> 00:09:15.250 line:80%
How so?

00:09:15.810 --> 00:09:17.810 line:80%
Right now, Zhao and that Mu boy

00:09:17.810 --> 00:09:19.410 line:80%
are the talk of the entire city.

00:09:19.860 --> 00:09:21.570 line:80%
If he proposes at this moment,

00:09:21.570 --> 00:09:23.380 line:80%
people will surely gossip.

00:09:24.170 --> 00:09:25.010 line:80%
And none of it

00:09:25.900 --> 00:09:26.860 line:80%
will sound pleasant.

00:09:26.860 --> 00:09:28.100 line:80%
That's precisely why

00:09:28.980 --> 00:09:31.100 line:80%
he must propose now.

00:09:35.380 --> 00:09:36.220 line:80%
Good.

00:09:36.570 --> 00:09:37.530 line:80%
That's responsibility.

00:09:37.530 --> 00:09:39.330 line:80%
A true son of the Song family.

00:09:50.020 --> 00:09:50.860 line:80%
The keys to

00:09:51.170 --> 00:09:52.010 line:80%
the storeroom,

00:09:52.220 --> 00:09:53.060 line:80%
the treasure chests,

00:09:53.220 --> 00:09:55.220 line:80%
the accounts office, and over a hundred estates

00:09:55.570 --> 00:09:56.410 line:80%
are all here.

00:09:58.570 --> 00:10:00.100 line:80%
Over a hundred estates?

00:10:00.100 --> 00:10:00.940 line:80%
Easy.

00:10:03.900 --> 00:10:05.450 line:80%
Lord Song, are you truly

00:10:05.450 --> 00:10:06.900 line:80%
going to propose for your son?

00:10:06.900 --> 00:10:08.530 line:80%
Such a serious matter,

00:10:08.530 --> 00:10:09.530 line:80%
how could it be a joke?

00:10:09.530 --> 00:10:11.050 line:80%
Rest assured,

00:10:11.050 --> 00:10:12.690 line:80%
if Zhao marries into our Guangtian Sect,

00:10:12.690 --> 00:10:14.530 line:80%
she will never suffer the slightest grievance.

00:10:14.780 --> 00:10:15.620 line:80%
Yes, yes, of course.

00:10:15.780 --> 00:10:16.810 line:80%
Though I have two sons,

00:10:17.140 --> 00:10:19.530 line:80%
everyone knows I favor the younger one.

00:10:19.860 --> 00:10:21.380 line:80%
His future wife would be

00:10:21.570 --> 00:10:22.440 line:80%
the one in charge

00:10:22.500 --> 00:10:24.020 line:80%
in Guangtian Sect.

00:10:25.290 --> 00:10:26.140 line:80%
Yes,

00:10:26.170 --> 00:10:28.020 line:80%
everyone knows you have a favorite.

00:10:28.930 --> 00:10:30.020 line:80%
But isn't it a bit soon

00:10:30.020 --> 00:10:31.100 line:80%
to propose now?

00:10:31.300 --> 00:10:32.140 line:80%
Yes, yes.

00:10:32.140 --> 00:10:33.570 line:80%
What about Mu Qingyan?

00:10:33.900 --> 00:10:34.740 line:80%
What did you say?

00:10:34.860 --> 00:10:35.810 line:80%
She mentioned Mu Qingyan.

00:10:38.410 --> 00:10:40.450 line:80%
It is perfectly normal

00:10:40.450 --> 00:10:42.860 line:80%
for a pretty young girl to have one or two

00:10:42.860 --> 00:10:43.810 line:80%
unreliable admirers.

00:10:44.500 --> 00:10:45.450 line:80%
That's good to hear.

00:10:48.540 --> 00:10:49.380 line:80%
Truth be told,

00:10:49.380 --> 00:10:50.260 line:80%
Yuzhi is

00:10:50.330 --> 00:10:51.170 line:80%
a good boy.

00:10:51.450 --> 00:10:52.290 line:80%
I like him.

00:10:52.660 --> 00:10:53.530 line:80%
But the problem is

00:10:53.530 --> 00:10:55.650 line:80%
Zhao just broke off an engagement.

00:10:55.650 --> 00:10:57.810 line:80%
To get betrothed again immediately...

00:10:57.810 --> 00:10:58.650 line:80%
Enough.

00:10:59.220 --> 00:11:00.290 line:80%
Pingchun,

00:11:00.740 --> 00:11:02.650 line:80%
you've roamed the martial world for years.

00:11:02.810 --> 00:11:04.450 line:80%
Haven't you heard the saying:

00:11:04.690 --> 00:11:06.500 line:80%
"A good girl has a hundred suitors"?

00:11:06.500 --> 00:11:07.340 line:80%
Isn't that right?

00:11:08.920 --> 00:11:09.780 line:80%
Stop reading.

00:11:09.780 --> 00:11:11.220 line:80%
Say something.

00:11:11.530 --> 00:11:12.370 line:80%
Yunke.

00:11:14.020 --> 00:11:15.170 line:80%
Yunke.

00:11:15.780 --> 00:11:16.780 line:80%
Say something.

00:11:17.100 --> 00:11:19.220 line:80%
Zhao and Yuzhi are a match made in heaven,

00:11:22.620 --> 00:11:23.460 line:80%
aren't they?

00:11:23.810 --> 00:11:24.900 line:80%
If they marry,

00:11:25.050 --> 00:11:26.380 line:80%
what could those people in

00:11:26.530 --> 00:11:27.540 line:80%
the martial world possibly say?

00:11:28.810 --> 00:11:29.780 line:80%
They are indeed

00:11:29.780 --> 00:11:30.780 line:80%
a good match.

00:11:32.100 --> 00:11:34.620 line:80%
But Zhao has always had a mind of her own.

00:11:34.930 --> 00:11:37.170 line:80%
She's just ended her engagement with Yuqi,

00:11:37.410 --> 00:11:38.610 line:80%
and now to promise her to someone else...

00:11:38.810 --> 00:11:41.290 line:80%
I fear she may not agree.

00:11:41.690 --> 00:11:42.860 line:80%
Let the young

00:11:43.050 --> 00:11:45.020 line:80%
handle their own affairs.

00:11:45.620 --> 00:11:47.450 line:80%
Rest easy.

00:12:29.500 --> 00:12:31.140 line:80%
Tri-colored peach blossoms?

00:12:48.650 --> 00:12:50.100 line:80%
Yuzhi, why did you ask me here,

00:12:51.100 --> 00:12:52.500 line:80%
and in such

00:12:53.330 --> 00:12:54.900 line:80%
a mysterious way?

00:12:55.330 --> 00:12:56.170 line:80%
Zhao,

00:12:56.900 --> 00:12:57.860 line:80%
I asked you here because

00:12:58.500 --> 00:12:59.740 line:80%
there's something I must tell you.

00:13:12.530 --> 00:13:14.100 line:80%
My father has asked Mr. Cai to let you
marry me.

00:13:14.570 --> 00:13:16.050 line:80%
But I need your consent.

00:13:18.140 --> 00:13:19.020 line:80%
You and me?

00:13:21.410 --> 00:13:23.020 line:80%
Lord Song is being utterly reckless.

00:13:23.900 --> 00:13:25.220 line:80%
That was my wish.

00:13:26.860 --> 00:13:27.700 line:80%
Zhao,

00:13:29.220 --> 00:13:30.220 line:80%
I care for you deeply.

00:13:44.530 --> 00:13:45.380 line:80%
I know.

00:13:45.690 --> 00:13:47.410 line:80%
Yuzhi, you want to help me out of
this predicament.

00:13:48.570 --> 00:13:49.410 line:80%
But I don't need that.

00:13:49.980 --> 00:13:50.930 line:80%
Aunt once said,

00:13:51.650 --> 00:13:52.860 line:80%
in life there are

00:13:53.220 --> 00:13:55.170 line:80%
hardships that you must face them yourself,

00:13:55.570 --> 00:13:56.650 line:80%
and no one can shoulder for you.

00:13:57.450 --> 00:13:58.380 line:80%
In the end,

00:13:58.380 --> 00:13:59.340 line:80%
we can only rely on ourselves.

00:14:00.410 --> 00:14:01.930 line:80%
I don't want to be a coward anymore,

00:14:05.290 --> 00:14:06.220 line:80%
hiding behind you

00:14:06.650 --> 00:14:08.050 line:80%
under the guise of marriage,

00:14:08.810 --> 00:14:10.220 line:80%
letting you bear the blame.

00:14:11.930 --> 00:14:12.770 line:80%
That wouldn't be fair.

00:14:13.220 --> 00:14:14.060 line:80%
Zhao,

00:14:14.740 --> 00:14:16.020 line:80%
I'm not trying to rescue you.

00:14:16.290 --> 00:14:17.500 line:80%
Thank you for your kindness, Yuzhi.

00:14:18.050 --> 00:14:19.100 line:80%
In my heart,

00:14:19.570 --> 00:14:21.140 line:80%
you will always be the best senior brother.

00:14:28.290 --> 00:14:29.130 line:80%
In that case,

00:14:29.810 --> 00:14:31.500 line:80%
you still owe me a bowl of

00:14:31.810 --> 00:14:32.780 line:80%
lotus congee.

00:14:54.330 --> 00:14:55.530 line:80%
Well, Yuzhi?

00:14:56.410 --> 00:14:58.410 line:80%
My lotus congee isn't bad, is it?

00:14:59.290 --> 00:15:00.930 line:80%
Do you know why I like lotus congee?

00:15:02.930 --> 00:15:03.930 line:80%
When I was young, I loved sweets,

00:15:04.810 --> 00:15:06.780 line:80%
yet Mother often made this for me.

00:15:07.380 --> 00:15:08.650 line:80%
She said lotus seeds clear the heart,

00:15:09.100 --> 00:15:11.330 line:80%
bitter at first taste, but sweet
in the aftertaste.

00:15:12.450 --> 00:15:14.050 line:80%
If one only wants sweetness,

00:15:14.050 --> 00:15:15.570 line:80%
pastries would do.

00:15:16.170 --> 00:15:17.980 line:80%
The "Smiley" my aunt made were delicious.

00:15:21.330 --> 00:15:22.330 line:80%
That lingering sweetness

00:15:22.980 --> 00:15:25.050 line:80%
may not be as direct as pastries,

00:15:26.450 --> 00:15:27.530 line:80%
but what if that direct sweetness

00:15:28.220 --> 00:15:29.740 line:80%
lasts only for a moment?

00:16:00.650 --> 00:16:01.690 line:80%
Are you out of your mind?

00:16:02.280 --> 00:16:03.140 line:80%
Do you know Master

00:16:03.140 --> 00:16:04.650 line:80%
and the others are searching all over for you?

00:16:05.050 --> 00:16:06.860 line:80%
You said "no set meeting,"

00:16:08.230 --> 00:16:09.500 line:80%
refused even to come down the mountain,

00:16:11.500 --> 00:16:12.450 line:80%
and here you are,

00:16:12.450 --> 00:16:14.500 line:80%
busy making lotus congee for someone.

00:16:18.380 --> 00:16:19.450 line:80%
What's it to you?

00:16:24.810 --> 00:16:25.900 line:80%
It concerns me.

00:16:27.620 --> 00:16:29.810 line:80%
The matter of the man in black isn't
settled yet.

00:16:30.530 --> 00:16:31.810 line:80%
I told you I'll find him myself.

00:16:33.780 --> 00:16:34.620 line:80%
Leave now.

00:16:34.740 --> 00:16:35.690 line:80%
If Master discovers you,

00:16:35.690 --> 00:16:36.530 line:80%
you won't be able to leave.

00:16:36.930 --> 00:16:37.770 line:80%
Why?

00:16:37.900 --> 00:16:38.930 line:80%
What do you mean, why?

00:16:39.140 --> 00:16:40.500 line:80%
Why did you suddenly change your mind?

00:16:41.290 --> 00:16:42.650 line:80%
What did your master tell you?

00:16:43.740 --> 00:16:45.070 line:80%
Is it that skin-painted demon story again?

00:16:46.930 --> 00:16:48.170 line:80%
Yes, the skin-painted demon.

00:16:48.900 --> 00:16:50.050 line:80%
He killed my aunt.

00:16:50.050 --> 00:16:51.530 line:80%
He killed her friends.

00:16:51.530 --> 00:16:52.740 line:80%
I cannot repeat her mistake.

00:16:56.450 --> 00:16:57.530 line:80%
But I'm not that demon.

00:16:57.860 --> 00:16:58.810 line:80%
Your aunt is your aunt.

00:16:58.810 --> 00:16:59.650 line:80%
You are you.

00:17:00.020 --> 00:17:01.140 line:80%
Why mix the two?

00:17:02.810 --> 00:17:03.740 line:80%
How do I know you're not?

00:17:04.700 --> 00:17:06.170 line:80%
The skin-painted demon excelled at disguise.

00:17:06.330 --> 00:17:07.500 line:80%
When you pretended to be Chang Ning,

00:17:08.050 --> 00:17:09.020 line:80%
no one noticed.

00:17:17.180 --> 00:17:18.020 line:80%
Zhao,

00:17:18.610 --> 00:17:20.330 line:80%
what must I do for you to believe me?

00:17:23.020 --> 00:17:24.500 line:80%
If you don't want to search for
the man in black,

00:17:25.180 --> 00:17:26.050 line:80%
then we won't.

00:17:26.570 --> 00:17:27.570 line:80%
We can abandon everything,

00:17:27.700 --> 00:17:28.710 line:80%
leave the martial world behind.

00:17:28.780 --> 00:17:29.850 line:80%
I have parents, family, friends.

00:17:30.090 --> 00:17:31.700 line:80%
Why should I abandon them for you?

00:17:32.530 --> 00:17:33.370 line:80%
Zhao.

00:17:35.290 --> 00:17:36.130 line:80%
Milady,

00:17:36.130 --> 00:17:37.090 line:80%
Lord Qi is here.

00:17:42.810 --> 00:17:43.650 line:80%
Master.

00:17:44.980 --> 00:17:46.020 line:80%
Father. Mother.

00:17:46.570 --> 00:17:47.420 line:80%
Zhao,

00:17:47.500 --> 00:17:48.540 line:80%
you're too young to understand

00:17:48.810 --> 00:17:50.700 line:80%
how treacherous the Demon Sect can be.

00:17:51.180 --> 00:17:52.020 line:80%
Leave this matter

00:17:52.460 --> 00:17:53.940 line:80%
to us adults.

00:17:54.420 --> 00:17:55.290 line:80%
Mr. Mu,

00:17:55.290 --> 00:17:56.780 line:80%
why aren't you out yet?

00:17:57.890 --> 00:17:59.050 line:80%
I wonder

00:17:59.530 --> 00:18:01.290 line:80%
what brings Lord Qi here.

00:18:29.050 --> 00:18:29.890 line:80%
Where did you

00:18:30.370 --> 00:18:31.330 line:80%
get this wrist guard?

00:18:32.700 --> 00:18:34.290 line:80%
It's a memento from my father.

00:18:35.460 --> 00:18:36.610 line:80%
Why do you ask?

00:18:36.610 --> 00:18:37.570 line:80%
Lord Qi?

00:18:37.940 --> 00:18:39.700 line:80%
Pingshu gave this to
the skin-painted demon.

00:18:40.290 --> 00:18:41.460 line:80%
I saw it with my own eyes.

00:18:41.740 --> 00:18:43.700 line:80%
So it was Mu Zhengming?

00:18:44.290 --> 00:18:45.130 line:80%
Qi,

00:18:45.460 --> 00:18:46.300 line:80%
what are you saying?

00:18:46.850 --> 00:18:47.690 line:80%
Skin-painted demon.

00:18:48.130 --> 00:18:49.500 line:80%
Your father is the skin-painted demon?

00:18:50.740 --> 00:18:51.580 line:80%
Lord Qi,

00:18:52.180 --> 00:18:53.050 line:80%
are you certain?

00:18:53.050 --> 00:18:54.130 line:80%
I would never mistake it.

00:18:55.290 --> 00:18:56.460 line:80%
The wrist guards on your arms

00:18:56.660 --> 00:18:57.890 line:80%
are the best proof.

00:19:05.890 --> 00:19:06.730 line:80%
Shangguan!

00:19:13.810 --> 00:19:15.340 line:80%
Zhao, wait for me.

00:19:26.810 --> 00:19:27.740 line:80%
Master,

00:19:27.740 --> 00:19:29.460 line:80%
was Mu Zhengming truly the skin-painted demon?

00:19:31.810 --> 00:19:32.890 line:80%
How could I lie

00:19:33.500 --> 00:19:34.700 line:80%
about your aunt's fate?

00:19:37.220 --> 00:19:38.060 line:80%
Get up.

00:19:40.570 --> 00:19:41.660 line:80%
I saw

00:19:42.130 --> 00:19:43.220 line:80%
that demon twice.

00:19:44.180 --> 00:19:45.460 line:80%
I will never forget him.

00:19:48.700 --> 00:19:49.810 line:80%
When I first met him,

00:19:50.980 --> 00:19:52.420 line:80%
my cultivation was still shallow.

00:19:53.090 --> 00:19:54.460 line:80%
While pursuing a villain,

00:19:55.180 --> 00:19:56.420 line:80%
I fell into a trap.

00:19:57.530 --> 00:19:58.570 line:80%
Your aunt rushed to save me.

00:19:59.180 --> 00:20:00.290 line:80%
In the midst of the fierce battle,

00:20:00.610 --> 00:20:01.850 line:80%
this man suddenly appeared

00:20:02.700 --> 00:20:04.220 line:80%
and lent us his aid.

00:20:25.400 --> 00:20:26.270 line:80%
What?

00:20:26.290 --> 00:20:27.370 line:80%
Do you find me too ruthless?

00:20:27.660 --> 00:20:29.460 line:80%
No. You are not ruthless at all.

00:20:29.460 --> 00:20:31.090 line:80%
On the contrary, I think you are like

00:20:31.780 --> 00:20:32.620 line:80%
wind and fire:

00:20:33.370 --> 00:20:34.370 line:80%
pure as the wind,

00:20:34.740 --> 00:20:35.890 line:80%
fierce as the fire.

00:20:36.460 --> 00:20:37.740 line:80%
It suits you perfectly.

00:20:39.050 --> 00:20:40.700 line:80%
(Righteous Spirit)
"Pure as the wind,

00:20:41.090 --> 00:20:42.500 line:80%
fierce as the fire."

00:20:43.810 --> 00:20:45.850 line:80%
So it was he who first said that.

00:20:45.850 --> 00:20:47.130 line:80%
In this martial world,

00:20:48.180 --> 00:20:49.940 line:80%
many admired your aunt.

00:20:49.940 --> 00:20:52.020 line:80%
Few truly understood her.

00:20:52.740 --> 00:20:53.980 line:80%
But he was different.

00:20:57.980 --> 00:21:00.370 line:80%
I saw this and thought it would look lovely
on you.

00:21:15.850 --> 00:21:16.940 line:80%
Irises.

00:21:17.330 --> 00:21:18.780 line:80%
They'll bring good luck.

00:21:28.500 --> 00:21:29.340 line:80%
Master.

00:21:29.530 --> 00:21:30.890 line:80%
But Mu Qingyan told me

00:21:31.330 --> 00:21:33.420 line:80%
Mu Zhengming
never left the Hanhai Mountains.

00:21:33.570 --> 00:21:36.370 line:80%
How can you trust the words of

00:21:38.290 --> 00:21:39.330 line:80%
It was my fault.

00:21:39.810 --> 00:21:41.020 line:80%
Otherwise,

00:21:41.530 --> 00:21:43.370 line:80%
your aunt would never have met him.

00:21:43.740 --> 00:21:44.890 line:80%
I was blind.

00:21:45.500 --> 00:21:46.500 line:80%
I failed to see

00:21:47.090 --> 00:21:50.740 line:80%
that he was a fiend wearing human skin.

00:21:52.980 --> 00:21:55.420 line:80%
I can't let you
walk the same path as Pingshu.

00:21:56.610 --> 00:21:57.460 line:80%
From today on,

00:21:58.570 --> 00:22:00.810 line:80%
you're not to take a single step
outside Qingque Sect.

00:22:01.780 --> 00:22:02.620 line:80%
If you dare,

00:22:04.330 --> 00:22:06.160 line:80%
don't blame me for
casting aside our master-disciple bond

00:22:08.420 --> 00:22:11.900 line:80%
(Righteous Spirit)

00:22:16.290 --> 00:22:17.890 line:80%
(My father could never be him.)

00:22:18.570 --> 00:22:19.570 line:80%
(Knowing his character,)

00:22:20.020 --> 00:22:21.660 line:80%
(he'd never do such things.)

00:22:25.020 --> 00:22:26.940 line:80%
(Then who is the owner
of this wrist guard?)

00:22:31.290 --> 00:22:33.660 line:80%
This is where my father lived as a child.

00:22:34.570 --> 00:22:35.530 line:80%
Two cradles.

00:22:37.220 --> 00:22:38.060 line:80%
Could it be...

00:22:38.220 --> 00:22:39.060 line:80%
Young Master,

00:22:42.090 --> 00:22:42.930 line:80%
Elder Yan has arrived.

00:22:43.130 --> 00:22:43.980 line:80%
Young Master.

00:22:44.050 --> 00:22:45.660 line:80%
Did my father have a brother?

00:22:54.390 --> 00:22:55.290 line:80%
You...

00:22:55.290 --> 00:22:56.420 line:80%
How did you know?

00:22:57.090 --> 00:22:57.930 line:80%
Where is he?

00:23:06.290 --> 00:23:08.050 line:80%
This was all Nie Hengcheng's doing.

00:23:08.460 --> 00:23:10.290 line:80%
Back then, after your grandmother,

00:23:10.610 --> 00:23:13.290 line:80%
Lady Ouyang, gave birth to twin sons,

00:23:13.740 --> 00:23:14.850 line:80%
Nie Hengcheng

00:23:14.850 --> 00:23:17.980 line:80%
presented the old chief with a stunning beauty.

00:23:17.980 --> 00:23:19.780 line:80%
Lady Ouyang, in fury,

00:23:19.780 --> 00:23:20.850 line:80%
left and insisted on

00:23:21.180 --> 00:23:23.940 line:80%
taking both young masters.

00:23:24.810 --> 00:23:25.650 line:80%
In the struggle,

00:23:25.940 --> 00:23:28.220 line:80%
the old chief managed to keep only your father.

00:23:28.220 --> 00:23:29.130 line:80%
Three years later,

00:23:29.130 --> 00:23:31.220 line:80%
he found your grandmother.

00:23:31.220 --> 00:23:33.700 line:80%
By then she was gravely ill, near death.

00:23:34.370 --> 00:23:35.210 line:80%
She said

00:23:35.810 --> 00:23:37.050 line:80%
the young master she had taken

00:23:37.050 --> 00:23:39.090 line:80%
had already died of illness.

00:23:40.050 --> 00:23:42.780 line:80%
The old chief was deeply shaken

00:23:43.050 --> 00:23:44.290 line:80%
and soon passed away.

00:23:45.050 --> 00:23:46.940 line:80%
Your father was still young,

00:23:46.940 --> 00:23:50.660 line:80%
so the sect's affairs fell into
Nie Hengcheng's hands.

00:23:51.700 --> 00:23:55.130 line:80%
In time, he usurped the position of Sect Chief.

00:24:01.660 --> 00:24:03.290 line:80%
Eternal Sacred Sect,

00:24:03.290 --> 00:24:05.090 line:80%
unify the martial world!

00:24:05.370 --> 00:24:06.780 line:80%
Eternal Sacred Sect,

00:24:07.020 --> 00:24:08.500 line:80%
unify the martial world!

00:24:08.700 --> 00:24:10.330 line:80%
Twenty years ago,

00:24:10.850 --> 00:24:13.610 line:80%
the other young master suddenly returned,

00:24:14.020 --> 00:24:15.530 line:80%
seeking to reclaim his inheritance.

00:24:16.100 --> 00:24:19.540 line:80%
(Mu Zhengyang, Li Sect)

00:24:37.020 --> 00:24:39.980 line:80%
Nie Hengcheng claimed he was an impostor

00:24:39.980 --> 00:24:41.660 line:80%
and sought to execute him.

00:24:42.530 --> 00:24:43.370 line:80%
Fortunately,

00:24:43.740 --> 00:24:45.810 line:80%
Young Master Zhengming intervened in time,

00:24:54.780 --> 00:24:55.780 line:80%
and Nie Hengcheng spared him.

00:24:57.290 --> 00:24:59.420 line:80%
At first, Nie Hengcheng refused.

00:24:59.780 --> 00:25:01.890 line:80%
But your father promised him

00:25:02.330 --> 00:25:05.130 line:80%
that he would never acknowledge Zhengyang.

00:25:05.130 --> 00:25:06.660 line:80%
Only then were they allowed to leave.

00:25:07.660 --> 00:25:08.850 line:80%
Nie Hengcheng even branded him here

00:25:08.850 --> 00:25:10.020 line:80%
(Abandoned)
"Abandoned"

00:25:10.020 --> 00:25:11.290 line:80%
before letting him go.

00:25:11.680 --> 00:25:12.530 line:80%
And then?

00:25:12.530 --> 00:25:14.610 line:80%
He likely hid deep in some remote mountains.

00:25:14.890 --> 00:25:17.660 line:80%
After that, I never heard of him again.

00:25:19.570 --> 00:25:22.130 line:80%
Young Master, why do you ask about this today?

00:25:22.700 --> 00:25:23.540 line:80%
Uncle Cheng,

00:25:25.020 --> 00:25:26.500 line:80%
Elder Yan has worked hard of late.

00:25:26.940 --> 00:25:27.980 line:80%
Have someone

00:25:27.980 --> 00:25:30.090 line:80%
fetch two jars of aged liquor from the cellar

00:25:30.740 --> 00:25:31.890 line:80%
for him to take back.

00:25:32.290 --> 00:25:33.610 line:80%
- Yes.
- Young Master...

00:25:33.610 --> 00:25:34.500 line:80%
Elder Yan,

00:25:34.500 --> 00:25:35.340 line:80%
please.

00:25:43.180 --> 00:25:44.020 line:80%
Uncle Cheng,

00:25:45.020 --> 00:25:46.180 line:80%
now it's your turn to speak.

00:25:48.570 --> 00:25:50.050 line:80%
Nie Hengcheng was meticulous.

00:25:50.940 --> 00:25:52.020 line:80%
He would never have allowed

00:25:52.020 --> 00:25:54.020 line:80%
an ambitious Mu heir to leave freely.

00:25:54.330 --> 00:25:56.180 line:80%
Father must have understood the stakes.

00:25:57.330 --> 00:25:59.130 line:80%
Where did he hide Mu Zhengyang?

00:25:59.130 --> 00:26:00.290 line:80%
He did indeed

00:26:00.290 --> 00:26:01.740 line:80%
hide Zhengyang

00:26:01.740 --> 00:26:02.850 line:80%
in a certain place.

00:26:03.220 --> 00:26:04.290 line:80%
Stay here for now.

00:26:04.810 --> 00:26:05.700 line:80%
Once the storm passes,

00:26:06.090 --> 00:26:06.940 line:80%
I will take you away.

00:26:09.740 --> 00:26:10.580 line:80%
Wait.

00:26:15.820 --> 00:26:19.180 line:80%
(Abandoned)

00:26:19.180 --> 00:26:25.580 line:80%
(Jiuzhou Archive)

00:26:30.660 --> 00:26:31.990 line:80%
(Abandoned)
Irises.

00:26:32.130 --> 00:26:33.530 line:80%
They'll bring good luck.

00:26:51.940 --> 00:26:52.800 line:80%
Uncle Cheng,

00:26:52.890 --> 00:26:54.220 line:80%
do you know where this man is now?

00:26:54.660 --> 00:26:55.610 line:80%
He's dead.

00:26:55.610 --> 00:26:56.450 line:80%
Dead?

00:26:56.850 --> 00:26:58.660 line:80%
About fifteen years ago.

00:26:59.530 --> 00:27:00.370 line:80%
At that time,

00:27:00.610 --> 00:27:02.810 line:80%
the Young Master had moved with you
to Carefree Chamber.

00:27:03.700 --> 00:27:04.850 line:80%
One day,

00:27:04.850 --> 00:27:05.940 line:80%
Mr. Chang

00:27:05.940 --> 00:27:08.740 line:80%
came to visit, bringing a frail young woman.

00:27:31.220 --> 00:27:32.290 line:80%
Did he leave

00:27:32.980 --> 00:27:34.090 line:80%
any last words?

00:27:37.290 --> 00:27:38.420 line:80%
He said nothing.

00:27:45.090 --> 00:27:46.460 line:80%
In a few more days,

00:27:47.370 --> 00:27:48.570 line:80%
I'll be seeing him myself.

00:27:49.090 --> 00:27:50.090 line:80%
I can ask for you then.

00:27:51.420 --> 00:27:52.260 line:80%
Don't talk nonsense.

00:27:58.810 --> 00:27:59.740 line:80%
I asked the Young Master.

00:28:00.570 --> 00:28:01.410 line:80%
He said

00:28:01.740 --> 00:28:03.330 line:80%
Zhengyang was already dead.

00:28:03.810 --> 00:28:04.740 line:80%
That woman

00:28:04.740 --> 00:28:06.130 line:80%
had only come to return his belongings.

00:28:07.530 --> 00:28:08.420 line:80%
Which means

00:28:09.890 --> 00:28:11.810 line:80%
no one can prove he ever existed.

00:28:15.180 --> 00:28:16.020 line:80%
Uncle Cheng,

00:28:17.290 --> 00:28:18.130 line:80%
did Mu Zhengyang

00:28:18.130 --> 00:28:19.130 line:80%
leave behind any other relics?

00:28:33.610 --> 00:28:34.460 line:80%
You're waiting for him.

00:28:35.610 --> 00:28:37.020 line:80%
Master has already ordered the Six Sects:

00:28:38.050 --> 00:28:40.420 line:80%
if Mu Qingyan steps out of
the Hanhai Mountains,

00:28:41.020 --> 00:28:42.090 line:80%
he is not to be spared.

00:28:42.700 --> 00:28:44.530 line:80%
I only hope he never comes.

00:28:46.180 --> 00:28:48.090 line:80%
But these past few days, you've lingered
at Fengyun Peak.

00:28:48.370 --> 00:28:49.210 line:80%
You are still waiting.

00:28:50.180 --> 00:28:51.660 line:80%
How do you know where I've been?

00:28:52.090 --> 00:28:53.220 line:80%
Master asked you to keep an eye on me?

00:28:54.290 --> 00:28:55.530 line:80%
Everyone is worried about you.

00:29:02.330 --> 00:29:03.180 line:80%
I am waiting,

00:29:04.180 --> 00:29:05.370 line:80%
but I'm not waiting for him.

00:29:06.740 --> 00:29:07.980 line:80%
I'm waiting for an answer.

00:29:12.290 --> 00:29:13.130 line:80%
Zhao,

00:29:13.420 --> 00:29:14.810 line:80%
the Ingenious Scholar said

00:29:15.090 --> 00:29:16.130 line:80%
these storybooks

00:29:16.130 --> 00:29:17.460 line:80%
are all the latest editions.

00:29:17.460 --> 00:29:18.820 line:80%
Have a look and see if you like them.

00:29:22.290 --> 00:29:24.220 line:80%
It's either a young hero meeting
a peasant girl,

00:29:24.700 --> 00:29:26.610 line:80%
or a rich lady marrying a scholar,

00:29:27.290 --> 00:29:28.290 line:80%
or perhaps

00:29:28.290 --> 00:29:29.890 line:80%
an immortal descending to earth,

00:29:29.890 --> 00:29:31.220 line:80%
stirring up life-and-death drama.

00:29:31.700 --> 00:29:32.610 line:80%
I'm tired of such tales.

00:29:35.780 --> 00:29:37.850 line:80%
What are these outdated stories?

00:29:38.290 --> 00:29:39.530 line:80%
Our Zhao isn't a child anymore.

00:29:39.530 --> 00:29:40.700 line:80%
What are you saying?

00:29:40.700 --> 00:29:42.460 line:80%
I picked these out with care.

00:29:42.460 --> 00:29:43.850 line:80%
All right, all right, I know, I know.

00:29:46.890 --> 00:29:47.860 line:80%
Zhao, look

00:29:47.860 --> 00:29:48.750 line:80%
what I have prepared for you.

00:29:48.760 --> 00:29:50.730 line:80%
Something new and solid.

00:29:51.130 --> 00:29:52.780 line:80%
A complete set of mechanisms:

00:29:53.460 --> 00:29:54.300 line:80%
a mechanical frog,

00:29:54.810 --> 00:29:56.020 line:80%
a mechanical grasshopper,

00:29:56.020 --> 00:29:57.180 line:80%
and this,

00:29:58.370 --> 00:29:59.500 line:80%
a mechanical bird.

00:29:59.500 --> 00:30:00.530 line:80%
Quite solid, indeed.

00:30:00.530 --> 00:30:01.570 line:80%
- Look.
- Madam,

00:30:01.570 --> 00:30:02.700 line:80%
Mr. Chang once gave Milady

00:30:02.700 --> 00:30:04.130 line:80%
a mechanical bird as well.

00:30:06.330 --> 00:30:07.170 line:80%
Xiaofeng,

00:30:07.290 --> 00:30:08.530 line:80%
the weather's nice.

00:30:08.530 --> 00:30:11.370 line:80%
How about a walk with me?

00:30:11.370 --> 00:30:12.330 line:80%
Pingchun,

00:30:12.330 --> 00:30:14.610 line:80%
I heard that Yin Sulian

00:30:14.980 --> 00:30:16.130 line:80%
has changed her ways lately,

00:30:16.130 --> 00:30:17.440 line:80%
spending her days in the Buddha hall,

00:30:17.440 --> 00:30:18.710 line:80%
eating vegetarian and chanting sutras.

00:30:19.090 --> 00:30:20.020 line:80%
Shall we

00:30:20.020 --> 00:30:20.940 line:80%
go take a look at her?

00:30:20.940 --> 00:30:22.290 line:80%
- Sure, let's go.
- Let's go take a look.

00:30:22.290 --> 00:30:23.620 line:80%
- Father, Mother.
- Come, Zhao.

00:30:24.420 --> 00:30:25.460 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:30:25.850 --> 00:30:27.500 line:80%
I won't repeat Aunt's mistake.

00:30:29.020 --> 00:30:30.420 line:80%
If he's someone I shouldn't love,

00:30:31.090 --> 00:30:32.050 line:80%
then from now on,

00:30:33.460 --> 00:30:34.460 line:80%
I won't.

00:30:36.290 --> 00:30:37.130 line:80%
Zhao,

00:30:37.290 --> 00:30:38.330 line:80%
you've always had your own mind,

00:30:38.700 --> 00:30:39.570 line:80%
bold enough to act your way.

00:30:40.180 --> 00:30:41.380 line:80%
Forget that skin-painted demon's son.

00:30:42.330 --> 00:30:43.170 line:80%
Forget him.

00:30:48.370 --> 00:30:49.940 line:80%
Reading some old clich├ęs now and then

00:30:49.940 --> 00:30:51.180 line:80%
isn't so bad.

00:30:51.180 --> 00:30:52.090 line:80%
Thank you, Father.

00:30:52.090 --> 00:30:52.930 line:80%
Thank you, Mother.

00:31:09.870 --> 00:31:10.740 line:80%
Young Master,

00:31:10.740 --> 00:31:11.810 line:80%
we've searched everywhere.

00:31:11.810 --> 00:31:13.530 line:80%
There's truly no trace of the relic
from those years.

00:31:15.330 --> 00:31:16.850 line:80%
(If Mu Zhengyang was the skin-painted demon,)

00:31:18.290 --> 00:31:19.130 line:80%
(then...)

00:31:19.610 --> 00:31:20.570 line:80%
My aunt came here?

00:31:20.940 --> 00:31:22.460 line:80%
She was searching for the saliva as well.

00:31:22.890 --> 00:31:24.130 line:80%
With her

00:31:24.660 --> 00:31:26.020 line:80%
was a masked man.

00:31:26.500 --> 00:31:27.340 line:80%
This painting

00:31:27.940 --> 00:31:29.530 line:80%
was done by him.

00:31:35.980 --> 00:31:37.660 line:80%
What unique wrist guards,

00:31:37.940 --> 00:31:39.050 line:80%
embroidered with two

00:31:39.740 --> 00:31:40.580 line:80%
irises.

00:31:42.420 --> 00:31:43.260 line:80%
Irises.

00:32:37.460 --> 00:32:38.300 line:80%
Young Master,

00:32:40.610 --> 00:32:41.450 line:80%
where are you going?

00:32:41.610 --> 00:32:42.450 line:80%
Qingque Sect.

00:32:43.330 --> 00:32:44.170 line:80%
She's waiting for me.

00:32:44.290 --> 00:32:45.130 line:80%
Young Master,

00:32:45.890 --> 00:32:47.180 line:80%
since Elder Hu was abducted,

00:32:47.570 --> 00:32:49.370 line:80%
many former members of the Xuanwu Altar
have defected.

00:32:49.370 --> 00:32:50.390 line:80%
Morale in the sect is unstable.

00:32:50.610 --> 00:32:51.980 line:80%
How can you leave at a time like this?

00:32:54.370 --> 00:32:55.740 line:80%
Since when did my affairs

00:32:57.330 --> 00:32:58.570 line:80%
become yours to manage?

00:32:58.570 --> 00:32:59.530 line:80%
In your eyes, Young Master,

00:33:00.220 --> 00:33:01.330 line:80%
is there only Miss Cai?

00:33:01.330 --> 00:33:02.330 line:80%
Is there no place for us?

00:33:02.700 --> 00:33:03.890 line:80%
Even if you won't think of us,

00:33:04.290 --> 00:33:05.390 line:80%
at least think of your own safety.

00:33:05.700 --> 00:33:07.180 line:80%
Qingque Sect is a deadly trap right now.

00:33:07.180 --> 00:33:08.220 line:80%
If you go,

00:33:08.220 --> 00:33:09.290 line:80%
your chances are slim.

00:33:09.700 --> 00:33:10.540 line:80%
Perhaps

00:33:10.740 --> 00:33:12.420 line:80%
we can send word by other means.

00:33:12.420 --> 00:33:13.700 line:80%
I must go in person.

00:33:14.130 --> 00:33:15.420 line:80%
Nie Zhe is watching like a hawk.

00:33:16.090 --> 00:33:17.740 line:80%
If anything happens to you,

00:33:17.740 --> 00:33:18.700 line:80%
then the sect chief's seat...

00:33:18.700 --> 00:33:20.020 line:80%
Then it changes hands again.

00:33:21.610 --> 00:33:22.450 line:80%
Whatever you do.

00:33:43.060 --> 00:33:44.100 line:80%
(Past and Future Glory)

00:33:44.130 --> 00:33:45.020 line:80%
A spy reports

00:33:45.420 --> 00:33:47.500 line:80%
"Strengthen defenses"
Mu Qingyan has left the Hanhai Mountains.

00:33:48.050 --> 00:33:48.940 line:80%
Even if

00:33:48.940 --> 00:33:50.050 line:80%
he has,

00:33:50.980 --> 00:33:52.570 line:80%
he may not dare come to Qingque Sect.

00:33:54.290 --> 00:33:56.570 line:80%
We're on full alert.

00:33:56.570 --> 00:33:58.610 line:80%
He must know that.

00:33:58.610 --> 00:33:59.940 line:80%
If this Young Master Mu

00:34:00.890 --> 00:34:02.530 line:80%
knew when to retreat,

00:34:03.050 --> 00:34:04.810 line:80%
he wouldn't have challenged Nie Zhe alone

00:34:04.810 --> 00:34:05.890 line:80%
in the first place,

00:34:05.890 --> 00:34:07.330 line:80%
nor reclaimed the Demon Sect

00:34:07.970 --> 00:34:09.370 line:80%
by his own strength.

00:34:09.780 --> 00:34:11.060 line:80%
If I'm not mistaken,

00:34:12.010 --> 00:34:13.540 line:80%
he'll come up the mountain tonight.

00:34:13.540 --> 00:34:14.700 line:80%
If he dares come,

00:34:15.010 --> 00:34:16.850 line:80%
he won't leave alive.

00:34:18.290 --> 00:34:19.370 line:80%
It's just Zhao...

00:34:38.370 --> 00:34:39.210 line:80%
Zhao.

00:34:41.850 --> 00:34:42.690 line:80%
Zhao.

00:34:45.540 --> 00:34:46.380 line:80%
Mother.

00:34:46.930 --> 00:34:48.370 line:80%
Come with me somewhere.

00:34:59.180 --> 00:35:00.700 line:80%
With this broken body of mine,

00:35:01.410 --> 00:35:02.330 line:80%
I'm afraid I cannot go.

00:35:02.580 --> 00:35:03.420 line:80%
Back then,

00:35:04.220 --> 00:35:06.450 line:80%
Zigui was closest to you.

00:35:06.970 --> 00:35:08.660 line:80%
This time, you must escort his ashes

00:35:08.660 --> 00:35:09.500 line:80%
back to Jiangdong.

00:35:10.890 --> 00:35:11.730 line:80%
Even if

00:35:11.970 --> 00:35:13.010 line:80%
we have to carry you.

00:35:16.410 --> 00:35:17.250 line:80%
Zhao,

00:35:17.660 --> 00:35:19.180 line:80%
stay here tonight.

00:35:19.180 --> 00:35:20.740 line:80%
Help your Uncle Lei pack.

00:35:20.740 --> 00:35:21.780 line:80%
We leave tomorrow.

00:35:24.010 --> 00:35:24.850 line:80%
I'm not going.

00:35:29.580 --> 00:35:30.420 line:80%
Lei Xiuming,

00:35:30.780 --> 00:35:32.810 line:80%
it's been eighteen years.

00:35:33.330 --> 00:35:35.370 line:80%
The one who harmed you has been found.

00:35:35.370 --> 00:35:36.620 line:80%
Are you going to hide on this mountain

00:35:36.620 --> 00:35:37.780 line:80%
for the rest of your life?

00:35:37.780 --> 00:35:38.620 line:80%
Uncle Lei,

00:35:40.010 --> 00:35:41.290 line:80%
was it Mu Zhengming

00:35:41.780 --> 00:35:42.780 line:80%
who ambushed you back then?

00:35:45.850 --> 00:35:46.700 line:80%
It was too dark.

00:35:48.490 --> 00:35:50.010 line:80%
Everything happened too fast.

00:35:51.490 --> 00:35:52.450 line:80%
I couldn't see clearly.

00:35:53.700 --> 00:35:54.540 line:80%
Enough.

00:35:54.740 --> 00:35:56.290 line:80%
Don't bring up the past again.

00:37:15.580 --> 00:37:17.330 line:80%
Who would have thought the dignified

00:37:18.540 --> 00:37:20.100 line:80%
Qingque Sect would use Thunderstorms?

00:37:20.410 --> 00:37:21.540 line:80%
Back then, Qingque Sect

00:37:22.330 --> 00:37:24.140 line:80%
confiscated many of them.

00:37:25.370 --> 00:37:26.620 line:80%
But the explosives are too vicious,

00:37:26.930 --> 00:37:27.850 line:80%
too underhanded,

00:37:28.330 --> 00:37:30.100 line:80%
so the sect disdained to use them.

00:37:30.930 --> 00:37:32.100 line:80%
Today, however,

00:37:32.100 --> 00:37:33.780 line:80%
they're perfectly suited

00:37:34.180 --> 00:37:35.620 line:80%
for Young Master Mu.

00:37:37.540 --> 00:37:38.700 line:80%
Mu Qingyan,

00:37:38.700 --> 00:37:40.850 line:80%
knowing it's a trap and still daring to come,

00:37:40.850 --> 00:37:42.100 line:80%
you've got nerve.

00:37:43.410 --> 00:37:44.370 line:80%
Where is Zhao?

00:37:44.850 --> 00:37:46.010 line:80%
She won't see you.

00:37:46.620 --> 00:37:47.460 line:80%
I advise you

00:37:47.740 --> 00:37:49.450 line:80%
to surrender now.

00:37:50.700 --> 00:37:52.290 line:80%
Enough talk.

00:38:51.540 --> 00:38:52.660 line:80%
You won't see her.

00:38:55.330 --> 00:38:56.810 line:80%
Let's see how long you can hold out.

00:39:09.290 --> 00:39:10.180 line:80%
Yunke,

00:39:10.780 --> 00:39:12.490 line:80%
the boy is stalling.

00:39:25.290 --> 00:39:26.130 line:80%
Zhao.

00:39:26.410 --> 00:39:27.250 line:80%
What is it?

00:39:29.850 --> 00:39:30.690 line:80%
Nothing.

00:39:32.430 --> 00:39:33.290 line:80%
Forget it.

00:39:33.290 --> 00:39:34.330 line:80%
Stop drinking tea.

00:39:34.330 --> 00:39:35.700 line:80%
Go help Uncle Lei pack.

00:39:35.700 --> 00:39:37.410 line:80%
Leave the jars and bottles,

00:39:37.410 --> 00:39:38.450 line:80%
just pack some clothes.

00:39:58.930 --> 00:39:59.770 line:80%
Mother.

00:40:00.930 --> 00:40:01.770 line:80%
What now?

00:40:02.330 --> 00:40:03.370 line:80%
I want to go back.

00:40:06.810 --> 00:40:08.140 line:80%
Back for what?

00:40:08.450 --> 00:40:09.330 line:80%
Feicui has

00:40:09.620 --> 00:40:11.290 line:80%
already packed your things.

00:40:11.490 --> 00:40:12.540 line:80%
Running back and forth

00:40:12.930 --> 00:40:13.770 line:80%
is such a bother.

00:40:17.850 --> 00:40:19.220 line:80%
Zhao, don't go.

00:40:21.330 --> 00:40:22.620 line:80%
Has he come?

00:40:30.890 --> 00:40:32.620 line:80%
You lured me away on purpose.

00:40:36.660 --> 00:40:38.010 line:80%
You're planning

00:40:41.180 --> 00:40:43.100 line:80%
to ambush and kill him.

00:40:46.410 --> 00:40:47.250 line:80%
Zhao,

00:40:47.490 --> 00:40:49.370 line:80%
your master and the others are furious.

00:40:49.620 --> 00:40:50.460 line:80%
Besides,

00:40:50.700 --> 00:40:51.930 line:80%
Young Master Mu is highly skilled.

00:40:52.410 --> 00:40:54.010 line:80%
He may have already escaped.

00:40:54.490 --> 00:40:55.620 line:80%
If he doesn't see me,

00:40:57.220 --> 00:40:58.290 line:80%
he won't leave.

00:40:59.890 --> 00:41:00.730 line:80%
Zhao.

00:41:02.200 --> 00:41:03.060 line:80%
Zhao!

00:41:03.060 --> 00:41:04.450 line:80%
They said it was all in the past,

00:41:05.290 --> 00:41:06.540 line:80%
but it's not over yet.

00:41:15.810 --> 00:41:16.650 line:80%
Stop!

00:41:19.930 --> 00:41:20.770 line:80%
Zhao!

00:41:24.920 --> 00:41:35.580 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:41:54.340 --> 00:41:58.750 line:80%
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

00:41:59.315 --> 00:42:03.930 line:80%
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

00:42:04.270 --> 00:42:08.835 line:80%
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

00:42:09.360 --> 00:42:13.660 line:80%
♪Free to wander in the world♪

00:42:16.605 --> 00:42:21.305 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:42:21.830 --> 00:42:26.120 line:80%
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

00:42:26.780 --> 00:42:30.810 line:80%
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

00:42:31.125 --> 00:42:36.250 line:80%
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

00:42:36.825 --> 00:42:41.635 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:42:41.850 --> 00:42:46.020 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:42:46.745 --> 00:42:50.680 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:42:51.180 --> 00:42:56.455 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

00:43:19.185 --> 00:43:24.315 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:43:24.680 --> 00:43:29.050 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:43:29.315 --> 00:43:33.445 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:43:33.630 --> 00:43:39.205 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪